---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
---

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1>Welcome to My Tech Blog</h1>
    <p>Exploring the latest in technology, one post at a time.</p>
    <a href="{{ '/blog/' | url }}" class="button">Read the Blog</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="home-content">
  <h2>About This Blog</h2>
  <p>This blog is a space for me to share my thoughts and experiences with the latest technologies. I write about a variety of topics, including web development, software engineering, and more. I hope you find the content informative and engaging.</p>

  <h2>Latest Posts</h2>
  {% set latestPosts = collections.posts | reverse | slice(3) %}
  <ul class="post-list">
    {% for post in latestPosts %}
      <li class="post-list-item">
        {% if post.data.thumbnail %}
          <a href="{{ post.url | url }}">
            <img src="{{ post.data.thumbnail }}" alt="Thumbnail for {{ post.data.title }}" class="post-thumbnail">
          </a>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="post-list-item-content">
          <h2 class="post-title">
            <a href="{{ post.url | url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
          </h2>
          <p class="post-meta">
            <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
          </p>
          <p class="post-excerpt">
            {{ post.data.description }}
          </p>
          <a href="{{ post.url | url }}" class="read-more">Read More</a>
        </div>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</div>
